<Base title="About — SIFT41" description="How SIFT41 curates: no sponsorships, no trends — just evidence, testing, and time.">
  <article class="page">
    <h1>About SIFT41</h1>

    <h2>Our Curation</h2>
    <p>SIFT41 started with a simple frustration: finding trustworthy recommendations shouldn't be this hard. So we built something different.</p>
    <p>We don't accept sponsorships. We don't chase trends. We investigate — comparing evidence, testing real-world performance, and waiting to see what holds up over time. If something doesn't prove itself, it doesn't make the cut. What remains is a curated set of recommendations we stand behind completely.</p>

    <h2>Monthly Edit</h2>
    <p>Each month, we spotlight one product we believe in completely — the one we'd tell a friend to buy without hesitation. This is our top pick, updated every month.</p>
    <p>We take our time. Every product is researched, tested, and lived with — and only what truly holds up finds a place here. These are the things we'd share with our closest friends.</p>

    <p class="note muted">Transparency note: Some links are affiliate links — we may earn a small commission at no additional cost to you. This supports our testing and research.</p>
  </article>
  <style>
    .page { max-width: 680px; }
